description:
This is a 15 minute workout called 'Pilates for Beginners - 15 Minute Beginner Pilates Workout' from the channel Jessica Valant.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Foundation Builder and The Comfort Moves vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This 15 Minute Pilates for Beginners Workout takes you through the basic Pilates exercises you need to feel strong in Pilates! It is a full body beginner Pilates workout perfect for anyone to do at home anytime.
